column5: Finally got my new motor all hooked up and gave her a test today to see if it runs. Click on the image for video.    Tomorrow I plan to get her out on the water for some break in time.
you seem happy it's working it's alive  the new Frankenboat
I would of thought you'd be more excited.lol.
Nice !!!! I like the new graphics too I was looking at a 250hp in the marina yesterday !!!! They are massive and mean lookin !!!! Cheers she will run awesome .....

Got her out for some on water testing and break in time for the new engine. Gotta say I'm pretty pleased so far. Need to do a bit of tweaking to the setup but it's almost where it needs to be. The Smartcraft gauge with troll control are the cats   !!!! With troll control you can vary the trolling speed 10 rpm at a time from 550 rpm to .................................. You can also set trolling speed by MPH/KPH if you have tricky or wavy cons.
You've got yourself a sweet set-up there now Dave, best of luck with it !!
Enjoy the new engine! Or is the motor???
you have to learn not to suppress your feelings Dave...  ....Congrates
Thnk i've seem thi movie before   "What Knockers !!!!!"   Great setup Dave !!!!!!
